snippet.title: Emz & Friends ©
snippet.description:
I am Emz who’s a Qualified Therapist & Life Coach. It’s my aim to offer support & guidance to people who struggle with day to day life, maybe you feel you cannot get help or it costs to much so I want to create a safe community where you find answers, help and support whilst connecting with other like minded people. 
I hope you will join our growing Bubble Family but have fun along the way. 🥰💜

If you’d like to support the channel by buying me a cuppa, follow me on Twitter and Instagram you can find all the links on the home page. 

love your Bubble sister 
Emz 💜
